{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.023.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">D\u00e9nombrement et peste<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. (1 Ch 21:1-6; 27:23, 24.) (2 R 20:12, etc. 2 Ch 32:25, 26.) Ps 81:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    La col\u00e8re de l\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019enflamma de nouveau contre Isra\u00ebl, et il excita David contre eux, en disant: Va, fais le d\u00e9nombrement d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.2","name":"2 Samuel 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.23.39","name":"2 Samuel 23:39","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.23.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Et le roi dit \u00e0 Joab, qui \u00e9tait chef de l\u2019arm\u00e9e et qui se trouvait pr\u00e8s de lui: Parcours toutes les tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, depuis Dan jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Beer-Sch\u00e9ba; qu\u2019on fasse le d\u00e9nombrement du peuple, et que je sache \u00e0 combien il s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.3","name":"2 Samuel 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.1","name":"2 Samuel 24:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Joab dit au roi: Que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, rende le peuple cent fois plus nombreux, et que les yeux du roi mon seigneur le voient! Mais pourquoi le roi mon seigneur veut-il faire cela?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.4","name":"2 Samuel 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.2","name":"2 Samuel 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi persista dans l\u2019ordre qu\u2019il donnait \u00e0 Joab et aux chefs de l\u2019arm\u00e9e; et Joab et les chefs de l\u2019arm\u00e9e quitt\u00e8rent le roi pour faire le d\u00e9nombrement du peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.5","name":"2 Samuel 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.3","name":"2 Samuel 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ils pass\u00e8rent le Jourdain, et ils camp\u00e8rent \u00e0 Aro\u00ebr, \u00e0 droite de la ville qui est au milieu de la vall\u00e9e de Gad, et pr\u00e8s de Jaezer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.6","name":"2 Samuel 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.4","name":"2 Samuel 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Ils all\u00e8rent en Galaad et dans le pays de Thachthim-Hodschi. Ils all\u00e8rent \u00e0 Dan-Jaan, et aux environs de Sidon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.7","name":"2 Samuel 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.5","name":"2 Samuel 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ils all\u00e8rent \u00e0 la forteresse de Tyr, et dans toutes les villes des H\u00e9viens et des Canan\u00e9ens. Ils termin\u00e8rent par le midi de Juda, \u00e0 Beer-Sch\u00e9ba.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.8","name":"2 Samuel 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.6","name":"2 Samuel 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ils parcoururent ainsi tout le pays, et ils arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem au bout de neuf mois et vingt jours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.9","name":"2 Samuel 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.7","name":"2 Samuel 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Joab remit au roi le r\u00f4le du d\u00e9nombrement du peuple: il y avait en Isra\u00ebl huit cent mille hommes de guerre tirant l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, et en Juda cinq cent mille hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.10","name":"2 Samuel 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.8","name":"2 Samuel 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-25: cf. (1 Ch 21:7-30. 2 Ch 3:1.) Ps 38. Jo\u00eb 2:14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>David sentit battre son c\u0153ur, apr\u00e8s qu\u2019il eut ainsi fait le d\u00e9nombrement du peuple. Et il dit \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel: J\u2019ai commis un grand p\u00e9ch\u00e9 en faisant cela! Maintenant, \u00f4 \u00c9ternel, daigne pardonner l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 de ton serviteur, car j\u2019ai compl\u00e8tement agi en insens\u00e9!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.11","name":"2 Samuel 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.9","name":"2 Samuel 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le lendemain, quand David se leva, la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut ainsi adress\u00e9e \u00e0 Gad le proph\u00e8te, le voyant de David:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.12","name":"2 Samuel 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.10","name":"2 Samuel 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Va dire \u00e0 David: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Je te propose trois fl\u00e9aux; choisis-en un, et je t\u2019en frapperai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.13","name":"2 Samuel 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.11","name":"2 Samuel 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Gad alla vers David, et lui fit conna\u00eetre la chose, en disant: Veux-tu sept ann\u00e9es de famine dans ton pays, ou bien trois mois de fuite devant tes ennemis qui te poursuivront, ou bien trois jours de peste dans ton pays? Maintenant choisis, et vois ce que je dois r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 celui qui m\u2019envoie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.14","name":"2 Samuel 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.12","name":"2 Samuel 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>David r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Gad: Je suis dans une grande angoisse! Oh! Tombons entre les mains de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, car ses compassions sont immenses; mais que je ne tombe pas entre les mains des hommes!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.15","name":"2 Samuel 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.13","name":"2 Samuel 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel envoya la peste en Isra\u00ebl, depuis le matin jusqu\u2019au temps fix\u00e9; et, de Dan \u00e0 Beer-Sch\u00e9ba, il mourut soixante-dix mille hommes parmi le peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.16","name":"2 Samuel 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.14","name":"2 Samuel 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Comme l\u2019ange \u00e9tendait la main sur J\u00e9rusalem pour la d\u00e9truire, l\u2019\u00c9ternel se repentit de ce mal, et il dit \u00e0 l\u2019ange qui faisait p\u00e9rir le peuple: Assez! Retire maintenant ta main. L\u2019ange de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9tait pr\u00e8s de l\u2019aire d\u2019Aravna, le J\u00e9busien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.17","name":"2 Samuel 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.15","name":"2 Samuel 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>David, voyant l\u2019ange qui frappait parmi le peuple, dit \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, j\u2019ai p\u00e9ch\u00e9! C\u2019est moi qui suis coupable; mais ces brebis, qu\u2019ont-elles fait? Que ta main soit donc sur moi et sur la maison de mon p\u00e8re!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.18","name":"2 Samuel 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.16","name":"2 Samuel 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Ce jour-l\u00e0, Gad vint aupr\u00e8s de David, et lui dit: Monte, \u00e9l\u00e8ve un autel \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel dans l\u2019aire d\u2019Aravna, le J\u00e9busien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.19","name":"2 Samuel 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.17","name":"2 Samuel 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>David monta, selon la parole de Gad, comme l\u2019\u00c9ternel l\u2019avait ordonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.20","name":"2 Samuel 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.18","name":"2 Samuel 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Aravna regarda, et il vit le roi et ses serviteurs qui se dirigeaient vers lui; et Aravna sortit, et se prosterna devant le roi, le visage contre terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.21","name":"2 Samuel 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.19","name":"2 Samuel 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Aravna dit: Pourquoi mon seigneur le roi vient-il vers son serviteur? Et David r\u00e9pondit: Pour acheter de toi l\u2019aire et pour y b\u00e2tir un autel \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, afin que la plaie se retire de dessus le peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.22","name":"2 Samuel 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.20","name":"2 Samuel 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Aravna dit \u00e0 David: Que mon seigneur le roi prenne l\u2019aire, et qu\u2019il y offre les sacrifices qu\u2019il lui plaira; vois, les b\u0153ufs seront pour l\u2019holocauste, et les chars avec l\u2019attelage serviront de bois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.23","name":"2 Samuel 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.21","name":"2 Samuel 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Aravna donna le tout au roi. Et Aravna dit au roi: Que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, te soit favorable!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.24","name":"2 Samuel 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.22","name":"2 Samuel 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.24","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:24","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.024.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Mais le roi dit \u00e0 Aravna: Non! Je veux l\u2019acheter de toi \u00e0 prix d\u2019argent, et je n\u2019offrirai point \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon Dieu, des holocaustes qui ne me co\u00fbtent rien. Et David acheta l\u2019aire et les b\u0153ufs pour cinquante sicles d\u2019argent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.25","name":"2 Samuel 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.23","name":"2 Samuel 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.25","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 24:25","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.024.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Kgs.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.24.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>David b\u00e2tit l\u00e0 un autel \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il offrit des holocaustes et des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces. Alors l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut apais\u00e9 envers le pays, et la plaie se retira d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24","name":"2 Samuel 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.1","name":"1 Rois 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Kgs.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.24.24","name":"2 Samuel 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.24.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbed8f1b4.42577604');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbed8f1b4.42577604\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbed8f1b4.42577604","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI